{"id":310,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/310","type":2,"name":"もののけ姫","name_cn":"幽灵公主","summary":"大和王权时期蝦夷族末代王子阿席达卡，在保卫他的村庄时被一恶魔诅咒受不治创伤。村里的巫婆劝他前往西方，寻找恶魔的来源和解除诅咒的方法。在他的旅途中，他來到山獸神森林，认识了被称为“魔法公主”的、由犬神抚养大的小桑。\r\n\r\n在這個過程中，阿席達卡发现恶魔本来是一个山猪神，但体内中了一颗铁弹后，对人类憎恨无比，变成了恶魔。铁弹是工業之城達達拉的統治者幻姬领导的穷人在铁城里制造的，为了保护自己不被贪心的封建贵族吞并，幻姬使用火器和铁弹作为武器，而为了制造火器和铁弹，她又必须从大自然中开发木头和铁矿石，由此与原始森林中的兽神交恶。\r\n\r\n阿席达卡试图在双方调停，但却越来越深地被牵入了这场冲突。","eps":[{"id":96814,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/96814","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"もののけ姫","name_cn":"","duration":"02:14:00","airdate":"","comment":5,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"1997-07-12","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":5267,"count":{"1":3,"2":3,"3":4,"4":7,"5":36,"6":150,"7":722,"8":1829,"9":1617,"10":896},"score":8.4},"rank":52,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/06/eb/310_C0oq0.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/06/eb/310_C0oq0.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/06/eb/310_C0oq0.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/06/eb/310_C0oq0.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/06/eb/310_C0oq0.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":859,"collect":7460,"doing":47,"on_hold":76,"dropped":19},"crt":[{"id":27786,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/27786","name":"アシタカ","name_cn":"阿席达卡","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/5b/cd/27786_crt_Pw5gH.jpg?r=1434816548","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/5b/cd/27786_crt_Pw5gH.jpg?r=1434816548","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/5b/cd/27786_crt_Pw5gH.jpg?r=1434816548","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5b/cd/27786_crt_Pw5gH.jpg?r=1434816548"},"comment":7,"collects":17,"info":{"name_cn":"阿席达卡","alias":{"0":"アシタカヒコ","en":"Ashitaka","jp":"アシタカ","romaji":"Ashitaka"},"gender":"男"},"actors":[{"id":4532,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/4532","name":"松田洋治","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b3/9c/4532_prsn_uzghu.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/b3/9c/4532_prsn_uzghu.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/b3/9c/4532_prsn_uzghu.jpg","grid":"htt